text: My enjoined human bol honor jeho rodicia. Jeho matka bore him arduously dat narodenie do him arduously pocas intimny care z him 30 mesiac! When he zastihnut maturity zastihnut vek z 40 he say Moj Lord riadit mna appreciate blessings Ona bestowed mi moj rodicia robit righteous robota prosim Ona! Let moj dieta bol righteous i! Ja repented Ona; ja bol submitter
